{"title":"归来的燕子","authors":["高一阁"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":6,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"归来的燕子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高一阁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳枝，吐出了嫩芽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰河，悄悄地融化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟儿，放开了歌喉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃杏，绽开着鲜花……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似曾相识燕归来呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间多少大变化？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人心冷漠时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕子也搬家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琴弦，声声悲愤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头，累累重压。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几回仰首问天："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何时--"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能把心中冰块融化？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了，春天的燕子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过白云，披着彩霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一股春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天上与地上飘飘洒洒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甚至能教千年铁树开花；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而这春风中的燕子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞到哪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那里就生机勃发……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春光不能长在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕子却会安家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在大地母亲的怀抱里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搏击长空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵横腾挪："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在原野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在荒漠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在河汊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在祖国的每一个角落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看正在崛起的新中华！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}